Absolutely delicious, and quite easy to make. However, this recipe is missing one key direction, which existed in the magazine version of Bon Appetit: You need to thinly slice the russet and sweet potatoes before they are spread in the baking dish! I reviewed this recipe on my own blog, Recipes That Worked by Mand Higgins.

