Rating: 3
The flavor was really good. The problem I found was the amount of cream--it ended up to liquidy. I would ease up on the amount of cream and stock and add some of the cheese into that mixture to thicken it up a bit. I would also put half the potatoes in the pan, pour some of the mixture on top to coat it, then put the rest of the potatoes down adding the rest of the mixture on top.

